      Subclasses of Alien in <Unnamed> 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  OneStepAlien
      OneStepAlien is a concrete subclass of Alien representing aliens; all aliens of this type move like a single entity from right to left or from left to right (they never go up or down, and at the beginning they move from left to right).
      class  RedSpacecraft
      RedSpacecraft extends Alien and represents a red space craft.
